---
import SupportInteractiveIsland from '#features/support/SupportInteractiveIsland'
import BaseLayout from '#layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="Support" canonicalPath="/support">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[40rem]">
    <h1 class="pb-4 md:pb-6">Support me!</h1>

    <div>
      <p class="pb-4 md:pb-6">
        Please consider support me if you appreciated the works I commissioned!
      </p>
      <p class="pb-4 md:pb-6">
        Commissioning such high-quality artworks at this pace made the entire project quite
        time-consuming and extremely expensive. Currently I found myself spending around 20k - 40k
        JPY on these each month. Therefore, any financial assistance you can provide, even a few
        dollars, would be greatly appreciated.
      </p>
      <p class="pb-4 md:pb-6">
        I&apos;m also thinking of replacing my very, very old car so I will be saving money from
        2024.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="pb-4 text-base md:pb-6 md:text-lg">Crypto Currencies</h2>

    <div>
      <SupportInteractiveIsland client:idle />

      <p class="hidden md:block md:pt-6 md:pb-6">Please click on the addresses to copy to clipboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 md:pt-4" />
    <hr />
    <div class="pb-4 md:pb-6" />

    <p class="pt-4 pb-4 md:pb-6">Thank you!</p>

    <p class="pb-4 md:pb-6">Please remember to follow and support the illustrators!</p>

    <div class="pb-6" />

    <a href="/" class="pb-4 md:pb-6">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
